"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1928303-olympics-2024-paris-argentina-mascherano\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  The start of2024 Olympicshave been marred by a series of burglaries, with two separate camps targeted by thieves.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 115, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Argentina's football team has had a particularly difficult start to the Games, suffering not only a controversial loss to Morocco in their opening match but also a break-in at their Lyon base.\", \"from\": 116, \"to\": 308, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 116, \"end\": 125, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999707151805, \"rank\": 2.8802411424046995e-08, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 238, \"end\": 245, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9998679276121026, \"rank\": 0.00013208915261094192, \"text\": \"Morocco\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 298, \"end\": 302, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympique_Lyonnais\", \"score\": 0.9996615680053405, \"rank\": 0.00033854656824148995, \"text\": \"Lyon\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympique_Lyonnais\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympique_Lyonnais\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Manager Javier Mascherano, formerly ofBarcelonaandLiverpool, revealed on Thursday that jewellery was stolen from their accommodation the day before they wereforced off the pitchdue to crowd trouble during their first group match on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 310, \"to\": 552, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 318, \"end\": 335, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Javier_Mascherano\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Javier Mascherano\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Javier_Mascherano\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Javier_Mascherano\"}, {\"begin\": 397, \"end\": 406, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jewellery\", \"score\": 0.9999999915894477, \"rank\": 8.410467424571214e-09, \"text\": \"jewellery\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jewellery\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jewellery\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a surprising turn of events, Argentina lost 2-1 to Morocco, despite believing they had scored a dramatic equaliser in the 15th minute of injury time at the end of the second half.\", \"from\": 553, \"to\": 735, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 585, \"end\": 594, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999707151805, \"rank\": 2.8802411424046995e-08, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 607, \"end\": 614, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9998679276121026, \"rank\": 0.00013208915261094192, \"text\": \"Morocco\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, as the team celebrated, projectiles and a flare were thrown onto the pitch, landing near the Argentine bench.\", \"from\": 737, \"to\": 855, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 839, \"end\": 848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999994562250891, \"rank\": 5.42208447644745e-07, \"text\": \"Argentine\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The match was subsequently suspended when several Moroccan fans invaded the pitch, prompting intervention from riot police.\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 979, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 906, \"end\": 914, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9985840412019794, \"rank\": 0.0007806557569745165, \"text\": \"Moroccan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Spectators were asked to leave the Saint Etienne stadium, and the players had to endure a nearly two-hour wait for the match to resume without any fans present.\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 1141, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"During this delay, it was announced that Argentina's equaliser had beendisallowed following a VAR review.\", \"from\": 1142, \"to\": 1247, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1183, \"end\": 1192, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999707151805, \"rank\": 2.8802411424046995e-08, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1236, \"end\": 1239, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.423935123171388e-22, \"text\": \"VAR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://d