outletBFMTVreported that jewellery worth around \\u00a342,000 was stolen, citing a judicial source.\", \"from\": 1864, \"to\": 1970, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1864, \"end\": 1870, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9598732054835308, \"rank\": 0.0363394946420794, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Argentina has since lodged an official complaint with FIFA's Disciplinary Committee over the pitch invasion amid concerns about the safety of their players.\", \"from\": 1971, \"to\": 2127, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1971, \"end\": 1980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999707151805, \"rank\": 2.8802411424046995e-08, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2025, \"end\": 2029, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"score\": 0.9999958999858258, \"rank\": 4.10003092494632e-06, \"text\": \"FIFA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Additionally, authorities have initiated an investigation into the theft of Almada's possessions.\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2225, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2204, \"end\": 2210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Almada\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.64622621516835e-15, \"text\": \"Almada\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Almada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Almada\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As it happens, the 23-year-old footballer is not the only Olympian to fall victim to theft this week.\", \"from\": 2227, 